ory:Populated places in V\u00e4sterbotten County]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Skellefte\u00e5 Municipality]]\n[[Category:Municipal seats of V\u00e4sterbotten County]]\n[[Category:Swedish municipal seats]]\n[[Category:Coastal cities and towns in Sweden]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: christianize \u2192 Christianize (2), 2014-2019 \u2192 2014\u20132019", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skellefte%C3%A5"}
